pre><span class="token key atrule">deploy</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="2"></td><td><pre>  <span class="token key atrule">type</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> git</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="3"></td><td><pre>  <span class="token key atrule">repo</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> git@github.com<span class="token punctuation">:</span>fairytalefu/fairytalefu.github.io.git</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="4"></td><td><pre>  <span class="token key atrule">branch</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> master</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="5"></td><td><pre>  <span class="token key atrule">message</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token string">"script auto commit"</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4创建github-page"><a class="anchor" href="#4创建github-page">#</a> 4. 创建 Github Page</h3><blockquote><p>注意：github 私有仓库创建 Github Page 是需要付费的。如果之前创建的是私有的，可以在 Github 的 Danage Zone 转换</p></blockquote><h3 id="5部署到github"><a class="anchor" href="#5部署到github">#</a> 5. 部署到 Github</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><figcaption data-lang="bash"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num="1"></td><td><pre>$ hexo g <span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo d <span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo s</pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6静态博客的痛点"><a class="anchor" href="#6静态博客的痛点">#</a> 6. 静态博客的痛点</h3><blockquote><p>1. 图床问题<br /> 2. 文章线上编辑</p></blockquote><h3 id="7hexo-常用命令"><a class="anchor" href="#7hexo-常用命令">#</a> 7.Hexo 常用命令</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><figcaption data-lang="bash"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num="1"></td><td><pre>hexo n <span class="token operator">==</span> hexo new</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="2"></td><td><pre>hexo g <span class="token operator">==</span> hexo generate</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="3"></td><td><pre>hexo s <span class="token operator">==</span> hexo server</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="4"